Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.00,0:03:21.68,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}挫けない
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.00,0:03:21.68,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}也不會氣餒
