Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.02,0:03:27.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}擦掉了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.82,0:03:28.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}擦掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.07,0:03:43.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}小圓
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.82,0:03:47.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}不快點吃掉的話可要遲到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.10,0:04:01.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}姐姐 怎麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.03,0:04:03.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}不…不好吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.79,0:04:07.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}不 很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.92,0:04:09.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}非常好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.96,0:04:14.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}活著才知道爸爸的早飯是這麼好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.30,0:04:18.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}然後啊 你聽我說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.01,0:04:21.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}都說了那麼多了還沒有注意到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.63,0:04:25.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}還說什麼「哎？什麼？我又說了奇怪的事情了？」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.05,0:04:26.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}一臉要哭出來的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.94,0:04:30.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}這邊可是拼命地在忍住笑啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.57,0:04:32.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}小爽 昨天的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.25,0:04:35.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}抱歉 現在別說了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.33,0:04:36.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}回頭再說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.93,0:04:48.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}的確適產年齡是以醫學根據為基準的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.61,0:04:53.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}但是從中來倒推出預計婚期是一個很大的錯誤
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.31,0:04:54.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}也就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.07,0:04:59.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}超過30歲的女性也有戀愛結婚的機會是理所當然的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.92,0:05:01.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}因此呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.16,0:05:06.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}這裡不使用過去完成式而是使用現在進行式才對…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.94,0:05:22.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}好像來到了別的的國度一樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.41,0:05:26.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}學校也好仁美也好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.15,0:05:29.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}明明應該和昨天相比完全沒有變化的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.68,0:05:33.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}卻好像身處在不認識的人群中一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.06,0:05:36.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}不認識的呢 誰都是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.68,0:05:39.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}魔女也好 麻美姐也好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.52,0:05:44.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}只有我們知道 別人一無所知
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.53,0:05:49.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}這不就等於在不同的世界裡看著不一樣的東西在生活了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.27,0:05:51.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}小爽…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.30,0:05:58.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}早在過去就改變了 我們早就該發現的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.61,0:06:07.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}小圓啊 現在還想成為魔法少女嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.93,0:06:15.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.96,0:06:18.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}沒辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.26,0:06:21.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}我也知道很狡猾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.97,0:06:24.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}直到現在來反悔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.98,0:06:27.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}但是 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.90,0:06:33.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}我現在只是想起那種死法就快要無法呼吸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.25,0:06:37.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}好害怕啊 我不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.14,0:06:45.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}麻美姐真的是個很溫柔的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.88,0:06:52.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}為了讓我們明白 戰鬥需要多大的覺悟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.67,0:06:54.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}那個人…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.94,0:07:00.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}吶丘比 這個城市會怎麼樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.15,0:07:06.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}以後誰來代替麻美姐從魔女手中守護大家呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.41,0:07:09.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}長久以來這裡都是麻美負責的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.16,0:07:13.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}一旦空缺的話別的魔法少女不會坐視不理的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.95,0:07:16.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}馬上就會有別的孩子為了狩獵魔女而來的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.37,0:07:21.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}{\pos(342,326)\fs16\b1}grief seed
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.37,0:07:21.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}可是那是只看上了悲歎之種才來的傢伙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.73,0:07:23.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}就像那個轉學生那樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.81,0:07:26.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}的確像麻美那樣的類型很少見
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.04,0:07:29.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}一般都會認真計較得失的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.79,0:07:31.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}無論是誰都會想要報酬的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.07,0:07:32.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}那…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.77,0:07:35.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}但是要指責的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.88,0:07:40.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}那是只有同樣身負魔法少女命運的孩子才行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.34,0:07:46.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}你們的心情我理解
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.57,0:07:49.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}雖然很遺憾 我也不能強人所難
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.68,0:07:56.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}那就此告別了 我也得去找需要和我訂契約的孩子了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.66,0:07:59.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}抱歉了 丘比
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.86,0:08:02.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}我才是 抱歉把你們捲進來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.04,0:08:06.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}雖然時間短暫 謝謝你們
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.69,0:08:09.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}能在一起很愉快 小圓
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.13,0:08:19.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.60,0:08:56.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.42,0:08:59.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}我是個軟弱的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.09,0:09:01.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.58,0:09:15.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}小炎…？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.68,0:09:25.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}你過於責備自己了  鹿目圓
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.76,0:09:30.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}沒有任何人可以責備你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.99,0:09:32.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}有的話 我是不會允許的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.71,0:09:38.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}你聽從了我的忠告了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.58,0:09:41.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.95,0:09:49.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}如果我早點聽小炎的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.34,0:09:52.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}即便如此巴麻美的命運也不會改變
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.01,0:09:57.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}但是你的命運卻改變了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.62,0:10:01.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}就算能拯救一個人 我也會很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.30,0:10:08.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}小炎啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.42,0:10:12.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}好像和麻美姐在不同的意義上都很老成呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.34,0:10:15.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}或許吧 我不否認
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.05,0:10:23.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}像昨天那樣有人死去已經看過很多次了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.44,0:10:25.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.55,0:10:28.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}有多少人了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.10,0:10:32.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}已經多到不想去數了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.67,0:10:38.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}那間房間 就一直那樣了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.88,0:10:43.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}巴麻美只有遠房親戚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.74,0:10:48.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}離出失蹤報告還有很長一段時間吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.90,0:10:52.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}誰都不會發現麻美姐死了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.22,0:10:55.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}沒辦法的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.03,0:10:58.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}在那邊死去的話 連屍體都不會留下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.26,0:11:03.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}這邊的世界裡 她就永遠是失蹤者了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.98,0:11:07.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}魔法少女的末路 就是這樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.36,0:11:22.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}太悲慘了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.76,0:11:30.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}明明是為了大家一直獨自一人在戰鬥的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.21,0:11:33.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}居然誰都沒有發現
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.38,0:11:36.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}這實在是太寂寞了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.97,0:11:41.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}就是靠這樣的契約我們才得到這種力量的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.10,0:11:44.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}不為別人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.79,0:11:48.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}是為了自己的祈願才戰鬥下去的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.61,0:11:52.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}就算誰都不會發現 就算被人遺忘
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.86,0:11:55.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}那也是沒有辦法的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.50,0:11:58.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}我會記住的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.04,0:12:03.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}麻美姐的事 我不會忘記的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.94,0:12:04.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}絕對不會
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.22,0:12:06.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.89,0:12:11.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}只要你這麼想 巴麻美就很幸福了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.07,0:12:13.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}幸福得令人羨慕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.57,0:12:19.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}小炎也是 我也不會忘記小炎的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.38,0:12:22.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}昨天你救了我的事 我絕對不會忘記的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.47,0:12:27.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}小炎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.13,0:12:30.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}你太溫柔了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.09,0:12:33.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}別忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.73,0:12:38.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}這份溫柔也可能會喚來更大的悲傷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.53,0:13:04.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}在聽什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.97,0:13:06.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}「亞麻色頭髮的少女」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.05,0:13:08.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}啊 德布西？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.17,0:13:10.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}這首歌非常好聽呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.70,0:13:17.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}我呢你看 這個樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.24,0:13:21.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}大家好像都會覺得我不是會聽古典的料
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.48,0:13:25.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}偶爾我說出曲名的時候 他們都會非常驚奇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.79,0:13:28.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}因為太意外而開始尊敬我了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.14,0:13:34.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}因為都是恭介教我的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.88,0:13:41.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}不然這些音樂我大概一輩子都沒有好好聽的機會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.40,0:13:42.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}小爽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.03,0:13:45.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.93,0:13:49.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}小爽是在玩弄我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.25,0:13:57.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}為什麼事到如今還要讓我聽什麼音樂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.15,0:13:59.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}是想故意讓我難過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.48,0:14:03.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}因為恭介喜歡音樂…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.81,0:14:05.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}我已經不想再聽了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.96,0:14:09.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}只能聽而不能自己演奏的曲子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.97,0:14:11.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}我… 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.02,0:14:26.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}動不了了 已經連痛覺都沒有了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.54,0:14:28.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}這樣的手…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.29,0:14:32.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}沒關係的 一定會有辦法的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.81,0:14:35.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}只要不放棄一定會有一天…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.59,0:14:37.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}說讓我放棄了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.33,0:14:42.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}叫我放棄演奏了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.14,0:14:45.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}醫生親自對我說的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.54,0:14:47.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}說憑現在的醫療水準是治不好的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.02,0:14:51.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}我的手已經不會再動了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.77,0:14:54.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}只要沒有魔法和奇跡存在的話是治不好的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.40,0:14:56.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.71,0:15:01.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}奇跡和魔法都是存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.61,0:15:19.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}小炎 明明好好交談的話也許可以成為朋友的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.96,0:15:23.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}為什麼會和麻美姐吵起來的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.72,0:15:25.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}咦？ 仁美…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.34,0:15:30.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}仁美 今天不用練習嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.42,0:15:36.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}那個 和那時的人一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.73,0:15:38.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}仁美
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.42,0:15:41.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}喂 我說仁美啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.80,0:15:45.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}哎呀 鹿目同學你好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.28,0:15:48.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}怎…怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.54,0:15:50.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}喂 你要去哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.93,0:15:52.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}你問哪裡 這個嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.63,0:15:57.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}是要比這裡好很多的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.43,0:15:58.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}仁美…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.99,0:16:02.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}啊對了 鹿目同學也請務必一起來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.59,0:16:05.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}對沒錯 這真是太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.95,0:16:11.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}怎麼辦 這難道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.03,0:16:28.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}如果能聯絡上小炎…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.99,0:16:31.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}不行啊 我不知道她的手機號碼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.92,0:16:39.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}是啊 我不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.95,0:16:44.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}連這麼一個小工廠都不能好好經營
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.16,0:16:50.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}現在這個時代 哪裡會有我的容身之處呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.46,0:17:02.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}聽好了 小圓
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.38,0:17:08.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}像這樣的東西如果使用不當的話後果會非常嚴重
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.81,0:17:13.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}我們全家都得領便當 絕對不能弄錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.20,0:17:16.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}不行 那個不行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.12,0:17:22.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}不能打擾 那是神聖的儀式哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.54,0:17:24.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}但是 那個很危險
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.09,0:17:27.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}這裡的人都會死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.19,0:17:33.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}沒錯 接下來我們所有的人都將踏上前往美好世界的旅途
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.70,0:17:36.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}你不知道這是多麼美妙的事情嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.87,0:17:39.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}活著的軀體只是個累贅
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.28,0:17:43.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}鹿目同學 你馬上也會明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.64,0:17:51.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.40,0:18:36.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}怎麼辦 怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.13,0:18:46.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}不…不要 這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.54,0:18:53.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}不要 救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.77,0:18:55.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}誰來救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.22,0:19:31.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}這是懲罰嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.94,0:19:39.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}一定是因為我太懦弱還說了謊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.64,0:19:44.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}所以受到了懲罰
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.25,0:20:05.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}小爽？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.99,0:20:22.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}這是最後一擊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.78,0:20:41.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}哎呀 抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.94,0:20:44.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}真是千鈞一髮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.56,0:20:47.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}小爽 這副打扮…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.53,0:20:53.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}那什麼 這就是心境的變化吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.79,0:21:00.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}沒事啦 作為第一次我幹得也算不錯了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.64,0:21:01.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.17,0:21:08.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}你…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.56,0:21:13.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}太遲了吧 轉學生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.97,0:21:44.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}沒想到你竟然會來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.16,0:21:51.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}我聽說麻美那傢伙掛了 才特地過來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.69,0:21:54.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}怎麼回事 這和說好的不一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.35,0:21:59.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}不好意思 這裡已經有新的魔法少女了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.60,0:22:01.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}雖然是剛剛訂下契約的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.68,0:22:04.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}這算什麼 超火大
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.22,0:22:06.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}但是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.77,0:22:12.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}我怎麼能把這樣一塊絕好的地盤交給剛出道的菜鳥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.72,0:22:14.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}你打算做什麼 杏子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.27,0:22:16.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}這還用問嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.84,0:22:20.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}總而言之 只要解決掉就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.17,0:22:23.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}把那女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.56,0:22:37.48,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,1000)\blur2\}曾經你在眼中燃起的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.56,0:22:37.48,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,1000)\blur2\}いつか君が瞳に灯す
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.49,0:22:41.19,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,1000)\blur2\}愛的光芒 超越了時間
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.49,0:22:41.19,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,1000)\blur2\}愛の光が 時を超えて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.19,0:22:45.16,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,1000)\blur2\}急劇毀滅的世界的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.19,0:22:45.16,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,1000)\blur2\}滅び急ぐ世界の夢を
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.19,0:22:48.88,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,1000)\blur2\}的確又一個 即將終結
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.19,0:22:48.88,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,1000)\blur2\}確かに一つ 壊すだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.88,0:22:51.68,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,1000)\blur2\}飲盡躊躇
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.88,0:22:51.68,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,1000)\blur2\}躊躇いを飲み干して
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.73,0:22:55.28,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,1000)\blur2\}你所期望的又是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.73,0:22:55.28,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,1000)\blur2\}君が望むモノは何
